{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "10-teachers-quizlock-frontend-integration",
    "name": "QuizLock API — 10. Teachers (Dashboard Enseignant)",
    "description": "Module 10 — Dashboard Enseignant\n\nTous les endpoints permettant de gérer les classes, les élèves et les collaborateurs :\n\n1. Gestion des écoles (Lister, rejoinder)\n2. Mes Classes & Statistiques\n3. Gestion des Etudiants et Invitations\n4. Enseignants Collaborateurs\n5. Annuaire (Chercher des enseignants)\n\n**Auth** : Cookie next-auth.session-token (login TEACHER requis)\n**Base URL** : {{baseUrl}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "classId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "À remplir en générant ou listant les classes"
    },
    {
      "key": "schoolId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "teacherId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "subjectId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Gestion des Établissements",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Lister mes écoles",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/schools",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teacher", "schools"]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/teacher/schools\n\nRetourne les écoles assignées ou demandées par l'enseignant."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2 Postuler à une école",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/link-school",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teacher", "link-school"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"schoolId\": \"{{schoolId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/teacher/link-school\n\nApplique à une école. Émet une requête PENDING."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Mes Classes & Statistiques",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "2.1 Lister mes classes",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (res.data && res.data.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('classId', res.data[0]._id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes"]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/classes\n\nRetourne la table principale des classes d'un enseignant (main + collaborateur).\nExpose le score moyen global et le sparkline (performanceHistory)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2.2 Créer une classe",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Terminale C - Maths\",\n  \"academicYear\": \"2024-2025\",\n  \"level\": \"ID_LEVEL\",\n  \"school\": \"ID_SCHOOL\",\n  \"field\": \"ID_FIELD\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/classes\n\nCrée une classe avec statut PENDING (si school) ou INDEPENDENT (sans school)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2.3 Détail d'une classe",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}"]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/classes/:classId"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2.4 Statistiques de la classe",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/stats",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "stats"]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/classes/:classId/stats\n\nExige d'avoir des étudiants et des examens complétés. Sinon retourne des données à 0."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Gestion Étudiants & invitations",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "3.1 Tous mes étudiants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teachers/students?search=",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teachers", "students"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": ""
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/teachers/students\n\nPool des étudiants de l'enseignant pour envoi de messages."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3.2 Retirer un étudiant de la classe",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/students/ID_STUDENT",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "students", "ID_STUDENT"]
            },
            "description": "DELETE /api/classes/:classId/students/:studentId\n\nRequiert isMainTeacher = true."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3.3 Obtenir liens invitation par défaut",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/invitations",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "invitations"]
            },
            "description": "Le crée si non existant."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3.4 Créer invitation spécifique (LINK)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/invitations",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "invitations"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"LINK\",\n  \"options\": {\n    \"maxUses\": 50\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Types : LINK, INDIVIDUAL, BATCH"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Enseignants Collaborateurs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "4.1 Lister collaborateurs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/teachers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "teachers"]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/classes/:id/teachers\n\nmainTeacher + collaborateurs."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4.2 Ajouter un collaborateur",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/teachers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "teachers"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"teacherId\": \"{{teacherId}}\",\n  \"subjectId\": \"{{subjectId}}\",\n  \"role\": \"COLLABORATOR\",\n  \"permissions\": [\"VIEW_STATS\", \"CREATE_EXAMS\"]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/classes/:id/teachers\n\nRequiert ClassTeacherPermission.INVITE_TEACHERS ou être prioritaire."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4.3 Mettre à jour collaborateurs",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/teachers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "teachers"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"teacherId\": \"{{teacherId}}\",\n  \"subjectId\": \"{{subjectId}}\",\n  \"permissions\": [\"VIEW_STATS\"]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "PUT /api/classes/:id/teachers"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4.4 Retirer collaborateur",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/classes/{{classId}}/teachers?teacherId={{teacherId}}&subjectId={{subjectId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "classes", "{{classId}}", "teachers"]
            },
            "description": "DELETE /api/classes/:id/teachers"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Annuaire (Recherche)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "5.1 Chercher enseignants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teachers?search=Prof&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teachers"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "Prof"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/teachers"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5.2 Créer un enseignant manuellement",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teachers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teachers"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nouveau Prof\",\n  \"email\": \"nouveau.prof@example.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/teachers\n\nCrée un utilisateur TEACHER inactif ou actif avec un MdP tmp."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5.3 Chercher enseignants externes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/teachers/external?subject={{subjectId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "teachers", "external"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "subject",
                  "value": "{{subjectId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/teachers/external"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
